Summary of Sales Feedback Issues

1. The company's self-developed products have slowed down, with no continuous updates, and equipment updates are too slow, all focusing on providing services;
2. 9B data does not have good positioning;
3. The company's products have been discontinued, front-end sales are not clear, lack of communication, lack of communication between the back-end and front-end, and many issues in delivery;
5. Poor delivery quality, difficulty in finalizing payments, accounts receivable accumulation affecting cash flow;
6. The company does not have a unified channel supplier for products, sales do not know which supplier's products to recommend;
7. An Tao Academy has not been updated for a long time, lack of training, has a certain negative impact on An Tao's brand, customers doubt whether the company is operating normally;
8. Testing of new products after launch is not ideal (Auxiliary Investigation Platform and Talent Empowerment Platform), customers are interested in the anti-fraud propaganda toolbox, but the product cannot be launched for a long time;
9. There are significant problems in the sales process, requiring submission of many complicated processes to cooperate, low efficiency in collaborative work, internal consumption;
10. The PPT is too long, customers do not understand, the PPT for districts and counties can be modified;
11. Sales project contracts are difficult to find, node reviews are complex, new employees have difficulty taking over work after sales personnel leave, it is recommended to use a sales CRM system to improve work efficiency, standardize sales processes, and currently, this work is being followed up and handled by Li Zhengxia.

